headline: Baxter to Present at Jefferies London Healthcare Conference
summary: DEERFIELD, Ill., November 13, 2024--Baxter International Inc. (NYSE:BAX), a global medtech leader, will present at the Jefferies London Healthcare Conference on Wednesday, November 20, 2024. Joel Grade, Baxter’s chief financial officer, is scheduled to present at 11:00 a.m. Greenwich Mean Time.
